Villarreal 's slide continued as a Diego Castro header gave Getafe a 1-1 draw in La Liga on Sunday but was overshadowed by a serious looking injury to Mateo Musacchio .
The Villarreal defender was carried off on a stretcher with 13 minutes to go after his ankle appeared to buckle when he was running for the ball .
The Argentine underwent a successful operation after being taken to hospital , he was diagnosed with a broken left ankle .
